<%@ page contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8" language="java" %>
<%@ taglib prefix="c" uri="jakarta.tags.core" %>
<jsp:include page="/jsp/common/header.jsp"><jsp:param name="pageTitle" value="Privacy Policy"/></jsp:include>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 120px; min-height: 80vh;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-primary);">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 40px;">Last updated: October 2026</p>

        <div style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-primary);">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">1. Information We Collect</h3>
            <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you create or modify your account, request on-demand services, contact customer support, or otherwise communicate with us. This includes your name, email address, phone number, postal address, profile picture, payment method, and items requested.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">2. Location Data</h3>
            <p>When you use our services for delivery, we collect precise location data from your device if you permit us to do so. We use this data to calculate delivery times, find nearby restaurants, and improve the delivery experience.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
            <p>We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our services, including to facilitate payments, send receipts, provide products and services you request, and send related information. We also use this data to personalize your experience and show you relevant offers.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">4. Sharing of Information</h3>
            <p>We share your information with the restaurant partners to prepare your order, and with delivery partners to fulfill your delivery. We do not sell your personal data to third parties for their direct marketing purposes.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px;">5. Data Security</h3>
            <p>We take reasonable measures to help protect information about you from loss, theft, misuse and unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration and destruction. We use industry-standard encryption for processing payments.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<jsp:include page="/jsp/common/footer.jsp"/>
